Top Nigerian actress, Mercy Aigbe is at the top of her game. She just announced a new Ambassador contract agreement with popular Nigerian Cargo Line, Adelove Shipping. The Number 1 Naija logistics Line, Adelove Shipping has a new face and voice. It has announced One of the best known Nigerian Actress, Mercy Aigbe as its logistics global brand ambassador, a partnership it says that will demonstrate the way the cargo company brand is ‘pioneering’ a new way for brands to engage with Naija Artists. The company announced the Nigerian Actress would be repping the Big Cargo company as its new global ambassador on September 28, 2020. The Super Actress, Mercy Aigbe who is amongst the Nigerian most influential people on the internet with numerous Awards and honours currently boasts over 8.7 million Instagram followers and this has made her a face to watch all around the business world. The partnership between these two powerhouses (Mercy Aigbe x Adelove Shipping) has officially begun with a digital campaign in celebration of the 2020/2021 collections. Spotlighted are the images taken during the contract agreement.  The partnership, which has been in the works was a no-brainer, according to Yemi Mustapha, Adelove Shipping Implementation Manager, who says the brand admired the Actress magnetic energy. “We were drawn to her confidence and fierce ambition as much as her power to hold nothing back”, Yemi says in a press release. The indigenous Nigerian Actress, Mercy Aigbe wrote in an Instagram caption announcing the partnership “Another Bag 💼 💰 secured! I am so honored to be part of this Number 1 Nigerian Shipping line @adeloveshipping family as I am taking up a big space on that carpet. Adelove Shipping ships both ways – from USA to Nigeria, and from Nigeria to USA, UK and Canada⁣
